This is an AI chat app meant to be run by individuals to access free models.

Notable architecture and components:

* SvelteKit app as the server
* OpenRouter for the AI endpoint, which follows openai API spec
* 1Password for secrets
* Secrets stored in .env
* TypeScript
* Tailwind CSS for UI components
* SQLite as the database
* Drizzle as ORM
* Vite for bundling and running
* Yarn for dependency management

Uses ESLint and Prettier for linting and formatting.
Do not use unneccesary semicolons in TypeScript code.